st important element of your site and the next important element is your sites look; even if you have these two you cannot do away with SEO.| You may feel that your website is built interestingly and has really good content so you don&#39;t require the services of an SEO consultant.}} when you {{decide | plan | wish}} to go in for internet marketing to reach your consumers then you realize that your presence on the web world is not as you have been expecting. Your voice through your website seems to get buried in the noise and the amount of traffic, leads and queries you expected, is nowhere to be seen. Precisely that is why you need an SEO consultant or a SEO firm or agency, who can bring you and your customers together, who can guide you in optimizing your presence on web so that your voice is heard above the clutter.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<br />\r\n	How SEO helps?</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	{{SEO consultants optimize your content by using right keywords in such a way that instead of being buried at the third page of the results after a search on the search engine, you are able to see your website and your web presence listed on the first page.|SEO consultants work on your site to optimize your keywords so as to keep your web site on the top page of search engines like Google and Yahoo.}} We {{generally | normally | usually}} look carefully at the search results present on the first page and are too lazy to go to the third or fourth page to check out the precuts and services listed there. {{It is really important that your web site beats other sites and take the first page position. | Hence from business point of view it certainly makes sense for you to be on the first page of search engine results.}} It increases visibility, more people click on it and the traffic increases.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	It is very important for you to find the right SEO consultant or SEO firm. There are many SEO consultants who use black hat techniques and take your site to the first page of search engine. These techniques bring your site on first page but such sites get banned and blocked by search engines. While hiring a SEO consultant you must find out whether the SEO company whould provide reoprts of rank and other analysis every week. Find out if they can guarantee that your site can be on the first page on at least a couple of keywords? You should not expect to be on first page with all your keywords. A good SEO consultant will provide a complete list of deliverables and the pricing model. Some companies and professionals will only provide you SEO services while others include email marketing, blog, podcasts, video links etc.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The SEO consultant whom you hire may make changes on your site. They would make soem changes in the meta tags and make changes in your content. They would incorporate keywords in your content. They will try to make it more search engine friendly so that the spiders or trackers of search engines are able to access the site and content with more ease. He will study and adjust the site architecture. HTML validation process will follow, and they could change the URLS, source codes, the Meta tags, etc. They will ensure that you have a good strategy as far as link programs are concerned. A comprehensive web page analysis will then follow which would be followed by a baseline report of the website. The Baseline report will provide the analysis of the keywords needed to drive the traffic. He will ensure that your presence and brand gets visibility and traffic.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'SEO, SEO consultant, ','How SEO helps?',NULL,NULL,NULL,35,27),(183,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Tuesdays can be hard too','<p>\r\n	Tuesdays can just be like Mondays sometimes</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Tuesday','Tuesdays can be like Mondays',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,19),(184,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Thursdays to look forward to Friday','<p>\r\n	Thursdays are great because its one day before Friday and the most busiest days of the week.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'thursday','friday is one day away',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,19),(185,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Travel with your pet','<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	You have a pet at home and can&rsquo;t leave it behind when you need to go for an international excursion How will you cute little animal live without you not being around? Even pets travel internationally but for their travel you need to make some vital arrangements. All countries have different rules for bringing and taking animals to and from the country. If you plan your pet&rsquo;s travel properly then you would not have any issues and have a happy trip with your pet.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Documents</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	The moment you plan to take your pet along, you should contact your destination embassy or consulate for information on pet import. Basic requirements would be international health certificate of the pet, pet passport etc. You must also find out what documents your country would ask for when you get back to your country. Most likely you would have to have a valid rabies vaccination certificate.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Veterinarian certification</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Get your pet checked up by your veterinary and obtain the certificates that you would need to furnish in the destination and country and back in your country too. You may be required to get your pet&rsquo;s health certificate certified by USDA. This certificate should be issued not more than two weeks prior to your departure.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"\">Microchip <o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p>Immigration officers need to compare the information on your pet&rsquo;s microchip to the contents of your</span> veterinary documents. So you should get your pet a microchip number. 9 to 10 digit microchip numbers are common in <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">America</st1:place></st1:country-region> but other countries ask for a 15 digit microchip number. I would suggest you better get a 15 digit microchip number. <span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span><span style=\"\">Pet&rsquo;s immunity<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p>If you are traveling to a rabies free country like <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\">England</st1:country-region>, <st1:country-region w:st=\"on\"><st1:place w:st=\"on\">Australia</st1:place></st1:country-region>, Japan etc then that country would require a blood titre certificate for you pet that would prove that the animal is immune to diseases like rabies.<o:p><br />\r\n	</o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"\">Airline<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"\">While you are in the process of finding out the required documents and certificates, you should also get in touch with the airlines that you would be taking. Properly inquire about the requirements. The airlines would also require certain documents. You might need to buy a pet carrier. Make your arrangements prior toyour travel date. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<span style=\"\">Hotel<o:p></o:p></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p>You should also contact your hotel or accommodation where you would put up so that they are able to specify the documentation they would require of you for your pet. This is an equally important aspect because the hotel is as important for you as getting entry into the country. <o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<span style=\"\"><o:p></o:p>Now that you are all set to travel with your pet keep in mind that you would have to mind your pet&rsquo;s actions. You love animals but that does not mean that other people also do. You will have to keep your pet with you and don&rsquo;t let it loiter here and there. Also keep your pet&rsquo;s collar with ID tags on at all times.<span style=\"\">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	&nbsp; <span style=\"\"><o:p><br />\r\n	</o:p></span></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'','',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,1),(186,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Saturday is a great day','<p>\r\n	While the barometer climbs it is tempting to skip all the other days of the week and make every day a Saturday. Saturday is beholden to morning cartoons and ice cream cones. Thus, making everyday a Saturday is a good idea.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Summer, weekends','Lazy days of summer',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,1),(187,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Test','<p>\r\n	test</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'test','test',NULL,NULL,NULL,44,19),(188,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hello','<p>\r\n	hello world</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'hello fhgkfg','djhgjkfg',NULL,NULL,NULL,44,19),(189,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Simple Live Smart Rules','<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{If you are health conscious then you can follow ways to live <leo_highlight id=\"leoHighlights_Underline_0\" leohighlights_keywords=\"smart\" leohighlights_underline=\"true\" leohighlights_url_bottom=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsBottom.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" leohighlights_url_top=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsTop.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" onclick=\"leoHighlightsHandleClick(\'leoHighlights_Underline_0\')\" onmouseout=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOut(\'leoHighlights_Underline_0\')\" onmouseover=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOver(\'leoHighlights_Underline_0\')\" style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 150); background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0% 50%; -moz-background-size: auto auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\">smart</leo_highlight> and be healthy for a longer period of time. | We all have desires to live <leo_highlight id=\"leoHighlights_Underline_1\" leohighlights_keywords=\"smart\" leohighlights_underline=\"true\" leohighlights_url_bottom=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsBottom.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" leohighlights_url_top=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsTop.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" onclick=\"leoHighlightsHandleClick(\'leoHighlights_Underline_1\')\" onmouseout=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOut(\'leoHighlights_Underline_1\')\" onmouseover=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOver(\'leoHighlights_Underline_1\')\" style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 150); background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0% 50%; -moz-background-size: auto auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\">smart</leo_highlight> and stay healthy but we can achieve such targets only if we are a little health conscious.}} Our eating, resting and moving habits are {{ruled | controlled}} by our {{temptations | desires}}. To lead a {{perfect | ideal}} life we need to {{rule over | control}} our {{temptations | desires}} and follow some simple rules but strictly. {{Everything is in your mind, so if you want to change your lifestyle then first make up your mind for the change. | If you really wish to bring a positive change in your life then you must first make up your mind.}} Once your mind is {{ready | prepared}} to follow {{rules | norms}} then there should not be any problem.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	{{Basic | Simple}} Live-<leo_highlight id=\"leoHighlights_Underline_2\" leohighlights_keywords=\"smart\" leohighlights_underline=\"true\" leohighlights_url_bottom=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsBottom.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" leohighlights_url_top=\"http%3A//shortcuts.thebrowserhighlighter.com/leonardo/plugin/highlights/3_1/tbh_highlightsTop.jsp?keywords%3Dsmart%26domain%3D\" onclick=\"leoHighlightsHandleClick(\'leoHighlights_Underline_2\')\" onmouseout=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOut(\'leoHighlights_Underline_2\')\" onmouseover=\"leoHighlightsHandleMouseOver(\'leoHighlights_Underline_2\')\" style=\"border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 150); background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0% 50%; -moz-background-size: auto auto; cursor: pointer; display: inline; -moz-background-clip: -moz-initial; -moz-background-origin: -moz-initial; -moz-background-inline-policy: -moz-initial;\">Smart</leo_highlight> rules</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	1. {{When you go to restaurants don&rsquo;t order high calorie drinks. | At a restaurant don&rsquo;t order any drink that has high calorific values.}} {{Drink water with your meal, it is not necessary to have those beverages. | With your meal order water that would not add extra calories.}}</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	2. {{Don&rsquo;t park your {{car | vehicle}} in front of your destination, park it a little behind so that you walk up to your destination | Park your {{car | vehicle}} {{at a distance | a little far}} so that you have to walk up a distance. }} {{I am sure you are lazy enough to go out for a regular walk so park your car away and take a walk. | You specially don&rsquo;t go out for walks so parking the car a little far may help you take a walk.}} This would help your limbs to move a bit.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	3. Breakfast like a king, lunch like a prince and dine like a pauper. Take your dinner early so that you don&rsquo;t go to bed soon after having your dinner. If you sleep soon after a meal then the calories don&rsquo;t burn and get stored as fat.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	4. {{Serve your food in a salad plate so that you serve less and ultimately eat less. | Serve small portions on your plate and eat slowly.}} If you fill up your plate then you have to eat too much and if you eat to fast then also you tend to eat more than required.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	5. Pick up the shopping bag and walk up to your local store and market for all household purchases. Move around and pick up things. {{Give your limbs a chance to move and work. | Your limbs would get another chance to move.}}</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	6. Avoid {{surviving on | buying | consuming}} packaged {{foods | edibles}}. Whenever possible {{go in for | buy | consume | eat}} fresh fruits and vegetables. Packaged foods have preservatives that are not good for health.<span style=\"\">&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	7. Take a balanced diet and don&rsquo;t starve your body. {{Your body should not feel that you are not getting enough food. | Don&rsquo;t let the body feel that it is not getting enough food to eat.}} If you keep your stomach full then it won&rsquo;t {{crave | ask}} for food and you won&rsquo;t end up eating {{too much | a lot | more than required}}.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	8. Become more active. Join a gym, play some sport, go out for morning walks or take out your pet for an evening walk.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	9. Reduce stress. Follow an exercise regime. Watch comedy television programs; go out with your family or friends. <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span>Discuss ideas and not people. Think positive and talk to people who are optimistic.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	10. Enjoy life for what it gives you and don&rsquo;t just hate your life for what it could not give you. Live in your present and for your future. Don&rsquo;t waste time {{crying over spilt milk. | thinking about the past.}}</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n	<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /></p>\r\n<