t a signature accessory but also a need for woman across the globe.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>Handbags for different occasions</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{Well, a woman would not carry the same handbag to office which she carries for grocery purchase and she would always have a different one that would match with her evening gown. You always have different bags for different occasions. You cannot carry the same bag to your workplace which you carry to the grocery store or you may not carry your party bag to your office.}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	1. {{Your office bag | The bag you carry to your work place}} should be medium in size and {{must | should}} have a number of pockets for {{different | various}} purposes. You should be able to keep you stationery in different pockets so that you don&rsquo;t have to {{dig | search}} your bag for a pen.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	2. {{You may carry a larger bag for shopping |For shopping you may carry a larger bag}} so that the bag serves your purpose and also is able to carry a few things that you {{buy. | purchase.}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p>3. If you are {{walking the red carpet | attending a formal party}} in the evening then you surely don&rsquo;t have to carry a huge bag. You just have to carry a small trendy bag that goes well with your {{outfit | dress | evening gown}}.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>Choice of bags</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	From colorful tote bags to leather handbags to trendy (and expensive) jeweled or beaded evening bags, the choices are endless. Some of the popular bags are evening bags, hobo style handbags, boxcar handbags, duffel and mini duffel handbags, shoulder bags and wrist bags.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>How to select a handbag</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>While selecting a bag don&rsquo;t just look for the style, examine the material. Bags carry too many things so they should be made of leather or other strong material. Check to see if there are no unfinished edges. Test zippers and clasps to ensure that they function properly. Examine any decorative trim such as beads, embroidery, iron appliqu&eacute;s or sequins. Ensure that there are no cracks, chips, splits or unsecured attachments.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'handbags, select a handbag, \r\n','selecting handbags',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,13),(191,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Handbags in fashion','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{Handbags are a fascination for women. | Women are fascinated by handbags. | Handbags are one of the most important accessories for women}} {{Look for bags in a woman&rsquo;s wardrobe and you would find different designs and different shades.| A woman&rsquo;s wardrobe is full of various designs and colors of handbags.}}{{Women {{generally | usually}} have different bags for different occasions and different dresses.| Women carry different styles of bags for different occasions and they also {{match | complement}} their bags with their dresses.}} A handbag contribute to the over all {{personality | persona}} of the woman and it {{enhance | boosts | adds to}} the elegance of her outfit. {{It is {{important | necessary}} that the bag {{complements | matches}} the dress. | the hand bag should always go well with a woman&rsquo;s dress and shoes.}}<o:p><br />\r\n	</o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	{{Need for Handbag | Handbag&rsquo;s purpose}}</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>Hnadbag is an elegant accessory but it is {{important |