e of bags</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	From colorful tote bags to leather handbags to trendy (and expensive) jeweled or beaded evening bags, the choices are endless. Some of the popular bags are evening bags, hobo style handbags, boxcar handbags, duffel and mini duffel handbags, shoulder bags and wrist bags.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>How to select a handbag</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>While selecting a bag don&rsquo;t just look for the style, examine the material. Bags carry too many things so they should be made of leather or other strong material. Check to see if there are no unfinished edges. Test zippers and clasps to ensure that they function properly. Examine any decorative trim such as beads, embroidery, iron appliqu&eacute;s or sequins. Ensure that there are no cracks, chips, splits or unsecured attachments.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<input id=\"gwProxy\" type=\"hidden\" /><!--Session data--><input id=\"jsProxy\" onclick=\"jsCall();\" type=\"hidden\" /></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'handbags, need for handbags,choice of bags, select handbags, ','Handbags in fashion',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,13),(192,NULL,NULL,NULL,'dog care','<p>\r\n	i love pets</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'dog','',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,19),(193,NULL,NULL,NULL,'happy','<p>\r\n	fhgfjgjfkgkkkk</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'adhkdsjhk','hdfjhdjdjhfdjfh',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(194,NULL,NULL,NULL,'h2','<p>\r\n	content</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'keywords','descrption',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,19),(195,NULL,NULL,NULL,'how to','<p>\r\n	content</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'keywords','descrption',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,19),(196,NULL,NULL,NULL,'parenting','<p>\r\n	aswfedscf</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'hsdjh','asasdf',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,19),(197,NULL,NULL,NULL,'TGIF ! ','<p>\r\n	Fridays in California are almost every day. One of the benefits is the opportunity to go from surf and sand to inland hot spots where wine grape grows</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Fridays are great','',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,12),(198,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Friday is a Great Day ','<p>\r\n	Just got the weekend newspaper with a listting of all the retail shopping sales and now its time to plan the weekend shopping spree with 50% off coupons in the newspaper.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'TGIF, Day of Week, weekend plans','What plans to make on Friday',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,13),(199,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Manish1','<p>\r\n	test</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'test','test',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,11),(200,NULL,NULL,NULL,'GearHoster','<p>\r\n	test</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'test','test',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(201,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Monday is a great day for Travel ','<p>\r\n	The benefit of traveling on Mondays is the best deal of the week as it is usually the slowest.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Monday','Traveling on Mondays',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,19),(202,NULL,NULL,NULL,'jdhfj','<p>\r\n	hfjdhf</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'jdgj','dhfdj',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(203,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Laitkor India','<p>\r\n	Laitkor India</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Laitkor India','Laitkor India',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(204,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Conserve Energy At Home','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{The big &lsquo;E&rsquo; Energy and the big &lsquo;S&rsquo; save together make &lsquo;Save Energy&rsquo;. | The big &lsquo;C&rsquo; Conserve and the big &lsquo;E&rsquo; energy together make &lsquo;Conserve Energy&rsquo;}}. {{Whenever I hear of Save Energy the first question that comes to mind is how and the next - &lsquo;will it actually help if I save energy&rsquo;? | I always wonder that how will it help if I save energy at home and even if I try to save then how. | Many a times we have many question about energy saving and try to find answers without taking steps towards saving energy}} I have {{learnt | gathered | experienced}} that every {{little | small}} step that I take to {{save | conserve}} helps to {{conserve | save}} energy. So why not we all start saving the amount of energy that we can save at our end without causing any discomfort? {{Following are a few ways by which we can conserve energy. | Here are a few ways to save energy at home}}</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	{{Conserve | Save Water}}</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{Conserve as much water as possible | Try to save as much water as possible.}} We live on water but we can&rsquo;t drown under it, so let only {{required | needful}} amount of water to flow in your house. {{Remember | Don&rsquo;t forget}} to turn off the taps. {{Take a shower but don&rsquo;t use gallons of water. | Don&rsquo;t waste too much of water while taking a shower, use as much required to clean and cool the body}} {{You require lots of water in the kitchen for washing dishes and for washing vegetables etc. but if make a conscious effort then you will be able to save a lot of water.| Lots of water is required in the kitchen for washing dishes etc and lots of water is used up for washing clothes but still you can conserve water while doing these chores too}} Don&rsquo;t let water flow into the drains, conserve it!</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Optimum geyser temperature</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{I won&rsquo;t ask you to take a cold water shower but keep the geyser temperature at an optimum level. Don&rsquo;t think I am asking you to take a cold water shower and punish yourself}} People normally fix a high temperature (that consumes a lot of energy) and then mix cold water to it. You actually don&rsquo;t need to heat the water to that level, warm the water for a shower, don&rsquo;t boil it!</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	{{Home Lighting | Lighting the Rooms}}</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{Markets are flooded with CFLs i.e. compact florescent lights that save energy and give out good light. | There are florescent bulbs called compact florescent light (CFL) that consume less energy and give optimum lighting.}} Before you change a bulb this time make sure you {{speak to | get in touch with | contact}} your electrician and get the energy saving bulbs. {{The energy efficient bulbs may be priced a little higher than the other bulbs they are worth the money | They may cost a bit more but if you keep the saving in mind then it is worth the money.}}</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Air conditioner</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Set the temperature of the air conditioners to something that is optimum, you don&rsquo;t always require the maximum temperature to be set. {{Switch of the air conditioner when you are not at home or maintain it at room temperature. | When you are not home either switch it off or leave it at room temperature.}} If you have a manual thermostat, just turn it up or down before you leave home. A little cautiousness from your side will show a huge lot of saving. When you are at hotels then also put off the lights etc. while moving out of the room. You pay for the room but you don&rsquo;t get the right to waste energy.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Put off the appliances</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{We must put off the electronic devices while we are not using them. | Many times we don&rsquo;t turn off the electronic devices when we are not using them.}}{{We can always make an effort to save energy. | The current that keeps loosing can be saved.}} When you turn of your computer or TV or music system just take a few steps and seconds to switch off the power too. Try this and see a huge difference in your next electricity bill.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Saving energy is so {{easy | simple}} and takes nothing out of you, neither time nor money, instead it reduces your bills. Make a conscious effort and start conserving energy for a better future.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'save energy, conserve energy, save water, home lighting, CFL, ','how to conserve energy',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,10),(205,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5 techniques to generate web traffic','<p>\r\n	<link href=\"file:///C:%5CDOCUME%7E1%5CLENOVO%5CLOCALS%7E1%5CTemp%5Cmsohtml1%5C01%5Cclip_filelist.xml\" rel=\"File-List\" /><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><style>\r\n<!--{cke_protected}%3C!%2D%2D%0A%20%2F*%20Style%20Definitions%20*%2F%0A%20p.MsoNormal%2C%20li.MsoNormal%2C%20div.MsoNormal%0A%09%7Bmso-style-parent%3A%22%22%3B%0A%09margin%3A0in%3B%0A%09margin-bottom%3A.0001pt%3B%0A%09mso-pagination%3Awidow-orphan%3B%0A%09font-size%3A12.0pt%3B%0A%09font-family%3A%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%3B%0A%09mso-fareast-font-family%3A%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%3B%7D%0Ap%0A%09%7Bmso-margin-top-alt%3Aauto%3B%0A%09margin-right%3A0in%3B%0A%09mso-margin-bottom-alt%3Aauto%3B%0A%09margin-left%3A0in%3B%0A%09mso-pagination%3Awidow-orphan%3B%0A%09font-size%3A12.0pt%3B%0A%09font-family%3A%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%3B%0A%09mso-fareast-font-family%3A%22Times%20New%20Roman%22%3B%7D%0A%40page%20Section1%0A%09%7Bsize%3A8.5in%2011.0in%3B%0A%09margin%3A1.0in%201.25in%201.0in%201.25in%3B%0A%09mso-header-margin%3A.5in%3B%0A%09mso-footer-margin%3A.5in%3B%0A%09mso-paper-source%3A0%3B%7D%0Adiv.Section1%0A%09%7Bpage%3ASection1%3B%7D%0A%2D%2D%3E-->\r\n</style><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n /* Style Definitions */\r\n table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	{{The number of web sites is augmenting with every passing day and hence building a highly competitive ground. | The sphere of internet is witnessing a mushroom growth of websites which in turn is augmenting competition.}} It is {{not easy | difficult}} to {{make money | earn | generate revenue}} through web sites; you need to have a module that is able to drive traffic and {{hold | glue | adhere}} them to your {{site | web site}}. {{Traffic can come to your site but the art is to keep bringing back the traffic hence your site should have content that interests your targeted audience.| It is easy to bring traffic to your site but to keep that traffic coming back you need to offer them quality}}</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	1. JV Giveaways</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Internet marketers set up a site to organize a JV give away event. They agree to use their lists to help build the lists of all the members involved. When a member participates in the event then that member gets a chance to increase the size of his list by taking advantage of the combined power of all the other participants. You just need to follow the rule of giving away free stuff in exchange of traffic / leads. All the members would submit their free stuffs together with the squeeze pages which are used to collect new sign-ups. This helps in building an email marketing list.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	2. {{Search Engine Marketing | SEO/SEM}}</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{Search engine marketing is a combination of a series of methods which when brought together help in generating backlinks for your web site.| Backlinks are very important for a web site to have a better position so with the help of Search engine marketing methods backlinks are generated.}} {{When your site is linked to other sites then it is deemed by the search engines that your site is valuable and this helps in improving the rank of your site. | Search engines look for sites that have backlinks, it is understood that those site which are linked to other sites are valuable. }} {{You may generate backlinks for your web site through the following methods: | You may use the following methods to generate backlinks:}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<strong>a. {{Article submission | Article marketing}}-</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	- you would need to write {{informative | educational | edifying}} articles {{related | that relate}}to the {{content | niche}} of your web site and get them published on the various article submission sites with a back link to the web site where you want the traffic to visit. Article submission is free and thus you don&rsquo;t have to bother about the costs. Even the top article submission sites are free for use but they accept only original articles.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>b. Directory submission-</strong> There are {{numerous | many | various}} directories where you can submit your site. {{Your web site&rsquo;s url is submitted on the web directory and you are able to generate one way links for your web site. | By submitting your web site url to the various web directories you get an opportunity to create one way links for your web site.}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>c. Press release-</strong> {{if there is something new and happening on your website and you want your audience to know about it then you must write press releases and submit them to the various press release sites. | Press release submission is just like spreading the news about something happening, so when you need to spread the word across about your web site then you may also submit press realeses.}} Even press release submission is free.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	3. Forum Marketing</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{Actively posting on forums gives you a great opportunity to build traffic on your web site.| If you are active on forums then you have a great opportunity to build links and generate traffic.}} <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span>When you put up questions or comment on questions on the forums you can place your signature along with the link to your website. {{Each time | Every time | Whenever}} you post on a forum you generate a back link for your site and you create better chances to attract few more visitors to your site.</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	4. Pay Per Click campaign</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	Pay Per Click is a form of advertising provided by search engine providers like (Google, Yahoo! and others) where you pay for top placement. {{Most search engines give top positions to the highest bidder. | If you are the highest bidder then you get the top position on the search engine}}{{You can generate high traffic to your website through a Pay Per Click campaign and get rid of optimization and link building | Pay Per Click campaigns help in generating high traffic without spending time on link building and optimization.}} You {{can | may}} have your {{ad | advertisement}}on the first page of the keyword search as listed in the search engines. {{This is not free | But you will have to pay for this}}. {{Every time | Each time | Whenever}} your link is clicked you have to pay for the click. You need to make a budget and monitor your account also. If your web site is new then I would recommend you not to go in for the PPC campaign. For beginners it is best to start with organic techniques.<span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	5. Affiliate marketing<br style=\"\" />\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><!--[endif]--></h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	For the products on your website it is best to try an affiliate program to {{attract | drive}} traffic. Your affiliates would drive traffic to your web site and in exchange they would take a commission on the sales.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Choose the best suited method for your web sites promotion and drive traffic to your website. The competition is tough and you have to {{sail through. | survive}} <strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></strong></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'SEO, SEM, web traffic, web ranking, JV giveaways, article marketing, press release, forum, pay per click, affiliate marketing,','5 techniques to generate web traffic',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,27),(206,NULL,NULL,NULL,'5 things that cloud hosting company must have ','<p>\r\n	<link href=\"file:///C:%5CDOCUME%7E1%5CLENOVO%5CLOCALS%7E1%5CTemp%5Cmsohtml1%5C01%5Cclip_filelist.xml\" rel=\"File-List\" /><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>\r\n  <w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n </w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n </w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><style>\r\n<!--{cke_protected}%3C!%2D%2D%7Bcke_protected%7D%253C!%252D%252D%250A%2520%252F*%2520Style%2520Definitions%2520*%252F%250A%2520p.Ms