t of th {{web | cloud}} host company can really live upto its claims or not. }} {{Among the {{thousands | hundreds}} of {{web |cloud}} hosts you have to {{choose |select | find}} the best for your business. <span style=\"\">|&nbsp; To select the best cloud host company for your business you must weigh all the provisions and limitatins of the host comapny.}} {{</span>You must be able to {{identify | find out}} the basic features offered and the then compare the cloud hosting companies on the basis of the features so as to find the best {{web| cloud}} hosting company. {{Here are five of the features you should look for to find the best web hosting company: | Look for some of the following features before you finalize a deal with a cloud host company: }}</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<em><b><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">1. Bandwidth</span></b></em></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{The amount of bandwidth you have determines how many visitors you can allow on your site. | The number of visitors who can visit your web site is determined by the bandwidth provided by the {{cloud | web}} host omapny. }} {{Many {{web | cloud}} host companies put a limit on the amount of traffic that visits your web site on a particular day.&nbsp; Sometimes cloud host provide you limited bandwidth that puts a limit on the number of your site visitors.}} {{It is difficult to provide a specified amount of bandwidth that you would require because it depends on the design and traffic of your web site. | For you, it may be difficult to specify a number of visitors to your site and in the long run you would not like to have a limited number of visitors}}<span style=\"\"> </span>The best web hosting companies should give you unlimited bandwidth when you choose a plan.&nbsp; {{If you find a company that wants to limit your bandwidth, you should save your money and look for a different company.| It is {{very important | vital}} for you to select a {{cloud | web}} host company that {{gives | offers}} you unlimited bandwidth so that you can serve unlimited traffic on a given date and time}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	<em><b><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">2. Disk Space</span></b></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	{{You place Files, Videos, and Pictures on your web site on the basis of the available disk space. | Disk space allows you to put files, videos and pictures on your web site. | With the available disk space you can sort your files, videos and pictures to put on your web site.}} {{An unlimited disk space provisison helps you to palce as many pictures and files as you wish. | You must look for a {{web | cloud}} hosting company that provides you with unlimited disk space.}} {{You {{might | may}} come across many {{cloud | web}} hosting companies that would put a limit on the disk space. | There are many web hosting companies that put a limit on the amount of disk space.}} {{If you contract with such a host company then you would have restrictions on the amount of content your put on your web site. | You have to choose rationally among the web hosting comapies so that you select one that gives you unlimited disk space.}} So it is {{best | rational | prudent}} to {{find | choose | select | hire}} a company that allows you unlimited disk space.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	<em><b><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">3. Domains</span></b></em><i style=\"\"><o:p></o:p></i></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	{{Depending on the plan that you choose your web hosting company will provide you with a hosting of unlimited domains under the same hosting account. | Any good web hosting company would allow you to host unlimited domains on one hosting account but it would depend on the plan you choose.}} While building a website, you may think that you only need a hosting account that allows you to host only one domain. If you {{select | hire |choose}} a web hosting company and plan that allows many domains then you won&rsquo;t have to buy separate hosting account for every domain that you acquire.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	<em><b><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">4. Uptime<o:p></o:p></span></b></em></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	{{You would want that your audience is able to visit your site at any hour, for this you need a web hosting company that guarantees uninterruped services. | The web hosting company guarantees to keep your website up for most of the times so that there is uninterrupted view for your traffic.}}&nbsp; Good web hosting companies usually have a guaranteed uptime of 99.9%&nbsp;which means that your website will be down less than 0.1% of the total time.&nbsp; It {{is not | may not be}} possible for a {{ cloud | web}} hosting company to offer a 100% uptime. You must {{check | take a over view}} sites that are running under the particular {{web | clould}} host company and see if they are up most of the time. <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span><b><i><o:p></o:p></i></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	<em><b><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">5. 24/7 Support</span></b></em><i style=\"\"> </i></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"\">\r\n	Placing your website under a web host company does not mean that you would not have issues. You must {{select | choose | hire}} the {{cloud | web}} host company that is able to provide you 24 hours support through live chats sessions or through emails. I would suggest that you should test the company&rsquo;s customer service before going into a contract with the company. <i style=\"\"><o:p></o:p></i></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	These are five features that any cloud hosting company would have in common. These features are not just the ones provided by web host companies but these are the most important and common features that any web host company should provide. <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span>Compare the provisions of the best web hosting companies and then select the one that suits your needs the best. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'best web hosting company, best cloud hosting company, bandwidth, disk space, domain uptime, ','5 things that cloud hosting company must have ',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,33),(207,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Science as a career','<p>\r\n	kjfdksf</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'add, article','test- add article',NULL,NULL,NULL,39,19),(208,NULL,NULL,NULL,'water','<p>\r\n	dfjd</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'sjfhd','',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(209,NULL,NULL,NULL,'vishu','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;add articleadd articleadd articleadd articleadd articleadd articleadd article add article add article add article</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'vishu','add article',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(210,NULL,NULL,NULL,'anu','<p>\r\n	jdfjkdfkdfjd</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'anu','anu',NULL,NULL,NULL,51,19),(211,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Good evening','<p>\r\n	<meta content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" http-equiv=\"content-type\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); \">\r\n	<p>\r\n		Good evening</p>\r\n</div>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Good evening','Good evening',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(212,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Mondays are good days...','<p>\r\n	When there is so much going on in the world sometimes the consistency of Monday morning going to work is a reassuring fact. You know where you have to be and when. Unless its Christmas or a legal governmental holiday Mondays are the days to start the work week and the perceived nausea induced headaches that come with the day on the calendar.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The other reassurance&nbsp; is that the copier needs paper, coffee pot needs to start, the phones need to be answered.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	So Mondays are good days.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Monday','Going to work makes Mondays good days',NULL,NULL,NULL,40,19),(213,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Dogs love flowerbeds','<p>\r\n	Over the weekend you went to the home improvement store and found a great sale on building your own garden with amazing flowers and plants that would really make your backyard look great!</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	After hours of clearing out the space, planting the florals and plants exactly 2 inches apart, and you properly water the garden you stand back and look at your accomplishment.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The family dog is nowhere near the area.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Then this morning you go out to sit on your patio, enjoy a cup of coffee and look over to your garden which is now a huge display of anarchy and dirt. The flowers are strewn about, the cute white fence that decorated the border of the garden is all eskew and then you see the culprit.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Your family dog looks up to you with those big eyes and his wagging tail having now found the bone he buried months ago underneath where you had just put your new garden.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	In a flash of lightening, you go from infuriated to laughing hysterics, what else would have happened, dogs love to roll in dirt.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Dogs, Flowers','Put in a garden and get dog dirty',NULL,NULL,NULL,58,15),(214,NULL,NULL,NULL,'jdfkhd','<p>\r\n	djkfhkdfd</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'jdfhkdf','',NULL,NULL,NULL,58,19),(215,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Go Fish! ','<p>\r\n	When planning a quiet, relaxing trip a burbling creek may just be the most serene place to find yourself relax. Of course, you may want to go do some fishing in a placid locale where you&nbsp;and the elements must compete like in Vermont Ice Fishing. Then you may find yourself on a little island out in the pacific looking a clown fish face to face in the waters off the&nbsp;Australia. The whole exercise of fishing is the serene qualities of just casting out your line and waiting for that knowing tug to reel in what has blessed you with its prescence.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	A very popular fish today that not only is easy to care for but indulges one to just sit and relax is the <a href=\"http://www.bettafish.com\">Betta fish</a>. The Betta fish are content with a little bit of food given and fresh water. While there are not schools of Betta fish to put into one large tank, one could easily decorate their workspace / home with assorted Bettas dotting their homescape. Another option is to get out of the house and go get dinner&nbsp;&nbsp;like taking a trip to &nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.alaska.com/\">Alaska</a>. You can find great deals for the place called an angler&#39;s dream. Literally, you can fish outside someone&#39;s office in downtown Anchorage. Each experience whether in home or outside in the wilderness can bring you a sense of relaxation unmatched.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Fish are very soothing and calm, at the Monterey Bay Aquarium one of their most popular displays is the <a href=\"http://www.montereybayaquarium.org/efc/kelp.aspx\">Kelp Forest</a>. In the display you will find bass zig zagging thru the kelp forest as Pacific Sardines dance while the Leopard shark gives you the side-eye not sure if you are staring at him or at the wolf-eels.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The basis when you think about your next trip, you may find your self staring at a Fish.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'fish, tropical, fishing hole, Alaska.com','Where to go fishing and see fish.',NULL,NULL,NULL,58,1),(216,NULL,NULL,NULL,'DarkStyled','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px; padding-bottom: 0px\">Darkddd testy</span></span></p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Meta keywords','Meta Description',NULL,NULL,NULL,3,19),(217,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Far and Away over there or Here? ','<p>\r\n	It is hard to get away from the strip malls and megaplexes today. It is tempting to shoot for the stars on <a href=\"http://www.virgingalactic.com/\">Virgin Galatic</a>, The Virgin empire expanded from records to outerspace because, well..I think Sir Richard Bronson might want to get away from it all. The space is our frontier where you can get the chance to look back at our small blue planet for just $200,000 it is more affordable than buying a house to a point. The down payment of $20,000 could go to a great car but then again the Virgin Galatic travels on a hybrid rocket motor. Bronson always the environmentalist.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	You rather stay earthbound but, still away from the screaming kids, find yourself in the <a href=\"http://www.virtualtourist.com/travel/Arctic/TravelGuide-Arctic.html\">Arctic</a> or the<a href=\"http://www.aot.com.au/\"> Outback </a>just help you get out there somewhere over there? Now you might want to go <a href=\"http://www.singlestravelcompany.com/\">alone</a>, just the <a href=\"http://www.best-romantic-vacations.com/adult-vacation-resorts.html\">two of you </a>, or bring the <a href=\"http://www.rowadventures.com/Family-Adventures.html\">whole family</a>&nbsp;there is a destination away from the strip malls and megaplexes. Planning is the most important step but, always try to be flexible like the <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0085995/\">Griswolds</a>&nbsp;in your effort to get away. The best time to travel is any day of the week and whenever the mood strikes you, but for the rest of us mortals, try to work out a financial plan with times and dates. If you are going to travel across <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0233142/\">North America </a>you won&#39;t be far from most services, but think about recreating an <a href=\"http://aroundtheworldblog.blogspot.com/\">adventure</a>. Be sure to take a few necessities with your Identity, clean clothes, and a <a href=\"http://adventure.howstuffworks.com/outdoor-activities/hiking/compass.htm\">compass</a>&nbsp;so you can always find your way home.</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'Space Travel, Australia, Alaska','Traveling to desolote places. ',NULL,NULL,NULL,58,19),(218,NULL,NULL,NULL,'testing articles','<h3>\r\n	<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-family: comic sans ms,cursive;\"><em><strong><span style=\"padding-bottom: 0px;\">Standard Format: {{A {{simple|basic}} example|An uncomplicated scenario|The {{simplest|trivial|fundamental|rudimentary