 table.MsoNormalTable\r\n	{mso-style-name:\"Table Normal\";\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0in;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{The number of web sites is augmenting with every passing day and hence building a highly competitive ground. | The sphere of internet is witnessing a mushroom growth of websites which in turn is augmenting competition.}} It is {{not easy | difficult}} to {{make money | earn | generate revenue}} through web sites; you need to have a module that is able to drive traffic and {{hold | glue | adhere}} them to your {{site | web site}}. {{Traffic can come to your site but the art is to keep bringing back the traffic hence your site should have content that interests your targeted audience.| It is easy to bring traffic to your site but to keep that traffic coming back you need to offer them quality}}</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	1. JV Giveaways</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Internet marketers set up a site to organize a JV give away event. They agree to use their lists to help build the lists of all the members involved. When a member participates in the event then that member gets a chance to increase the size of his list by taking advantage of the combined power of all the other participants. You just need to follow the rule of giving away free stuff in exchange of traffic / leads. All the members would submit their free stuffs together with the squeeze pages which are used to collect new sign-ups. This helps in building an email marketing list.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	2. {{Search Engine Marketing | SEO/SEM}}</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{Search engine marketing is a combination of a series of methods which when brought together help in generating backlinks for your web site.| Backlinks are very important for a web site to have a better position so with the help of Search engine marketing methods backlinks are generated.}} {{When your site is linked to other sites then it is deemed by the search engines that your site is valuable and this helps in improving the rank of your site. | Search engines look for sites that have backlinks, it is understood that those site which are linked to other sites are valuable. }} {{You may generate backlinks for your web site through the following methods: | You may use the following methods to generate backlinks:}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>a. {{Article submission | Article marketing}}-</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	- you would need to write {{informative | educational | edifying}} articles {{related | that relate}}to the {{content | niche}} of your web site and get them published on the various article submission sites with a back link to the web site where you want the traffic to visit. Article submission is free and thus you don&rsquo;t have to bother about the costs. Even the top article submission sites are free for use but they accept only original articles.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>b. Directory submission-</strong> There are {{numerous | many | various}} directories where you can submit your site. {{Your web site&rsquo;s url is submitted on the web directory and you are able to generate one way links for your web site. | By submitting your web site url to the various web directories you get an opportunity to create one way links for your web site.}}</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n	<strong>c. Press release-</strong> {{if there is something new and happening on your website and you want your audience to know about it then you must write press releases and submit them to the various press release sites. | Press release submission is just like spreading the news about something happening, so when you need to spread the word across about your web site then you may also submit press realeses.}} Even press release submission is free.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	3. Forum Marketing</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{Actively posting on forums gives you a great opportunity to build traffic on your web site.| If you are active on forums then you have a great opportunity to build links and generate traffic.}} <span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span>When you put up questions or comment on questions on the forums you can place your signature along with the link to your website. {{Each time | Every time | Whenever}} you post on a forum you generate a back link for your site and you create better chances to attract few more visitors to your site.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	4. Pay Per Click campaign</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Pay Per Click is a form of advertising provided by search engine providers like (Google, Yahoo! and others) where you pay for top placement. {{Most search engines give top positions to the highest bidder. | If you are the highest bidder then you get the top position on the search engine}}{{You can generate high traffic to your website through a Pay Per Click campaign and get rid of optimization and link building | Pay Per Click campaigns help in generating high traffic without spending time on link building and optimization.}} You {{can | may}} have your {{ad | advertisement}}on the first page of the keyword search as listed in the search engines. {{This is not free | But you will have to pay for this}}. {{Every time | Each time | Whenever}} your link is clicked you have to pay for the click. You need to make a budget and monitor your account also. If your web site is new then I would recommend you not to go in for the PPC campaign. For beginners it is best to start with organic techniques.<span style=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	5. Affiliate marketing<br style=\"\" />\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><!--[endif]--></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	For the products on your website it is best to try an affiliate program to {{attract | drive}} traffic. Your affiliates would drive traffic to your web site and in exchange they would take a commission on the sales.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Choose the best suited method for your web sites promotion and drive traffic to your website. The competition is tough and you have to {{sail through. | survive}} <strong><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><o:p></o:p></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<link href=\"file:///C:%5CDOCUME%7E1%5CLENOVO%5CLOCALS%7E1%5CTemp%5Cmsohtml1%5C01%5Cclip_filelist.xml\" rel=\"File-List\" /><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n  <w:PunctuationKerning/>\r\n  <w:ValidateAgainstSchemas/>\r\n  <w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n  <w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n  <w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n  <w:Compatibility>\r\n   <w:BreakWrappedTables/>\r\n   <w:SnapToGridInCell/>\r\n   <w:WrapTextWithPunct/>\r\n   <w:UseAsianBreakRules/>\r\n   <w:DontGrowAutofit/>\r\n  </w:Compatibility>