optimizing a site with all of the major search engines.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>How search engines work<o:p><br />\r\n	</o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	You {{must | need}} to have an {{comprehension | understanding}} of how a search engine works. {{When a user seeks information the user searches the web using his favourite search engine.| Any user searches the web for information through search engines.}} The search keyword varies a great deal and, in today&#39;s crowded web world, could be found in countless pages. {{Sites are ranked i order to show then in a proper order. | Thanks to this, sites need to be ranked in order to show them in a uniform fashion.}}<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p>Search engines have different criteria whilst these can vary from engine to engine, there are standards that most prescribe to. Some of them are backlinks, keyword placement, Meta tags, <st1:place w:st=\"on\">Meta</st1:place> description, keyword density, unique content, age of the page, frequency of update and many more. Based on these criteria a search engine determines the ranking of a site.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Content<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{{{Earlier | sometime back}} content was made up of nothing much more than repeated keywords. A few years back content was built on repeted keywords}} Today&#39;s major search engines however, are refined enough to distinguish between real and fake characteristics of a page. {{The challenge to search engine optimization experts is to fulfil these criteria in a way that seems real to the search engines and is useful to users.| Search engine optimization experts make site&#39;s content appear real and origional to search engines and also useful to users.}}<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>SEO Techniques<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>{{The search engine optimization process is done in two different ways; inside the site (on page) and outside the site (off page).| There are broadly two search engine optimisation techniques : onpage optimization and off-page optimization.}}<span style=\"\">&nbsp; </span>{{Internally, the steps taken | On page optimization}} include content modification, <st1:place w:st=\"on\">Meta</st1:place> tag, size and placement of keywords and more. When ranking a site, search engines analyse the number of occurrence of the keywords, the relative distance between the keywords, size of keyword text, relevance with the content and even more factors.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{Off page SEO techniques are used outsite the website.| The second part takes place outside the site.}} {{The best way to handle off page SEO is to build links.| This most often includes working with backlinks.}} Backlinks are the external links that point towards your site. {{If the host site has a good rank thent he quality of the back link is also considered good. | The quality of backlink depends upon the rank of the host site.}} A link from a site with page rank 4 is much more valuable than the backlink from a page rank 0 site. Search engines can detect spams, so placing spammy comments which link to different sites is not effective in the search engine optimisation process.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	Anchor Text<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{You cannot give backlinks without considering the anchor text. | The Anchor texts of the backlinks are another important factor in SEO services. | It is very important to use the keywords as the anchor text.}} {{If you use |Use of relevant but}} different anchor texts can increase the ranking. {{It is important to use large font sizes and also header tags |Use of large font size and use of bold, italic or underlined text can also do the same.}}</p>\r\n',NULL,NULL,'How Search Engines Work','How Search Engines Work',NULL,NULL,NULL,58,27),(240,NULL,NULL,NULL,'How Search Engines Function','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	{{Search engine optimization (SEO) services, are the {{processes |services}} that {{work | are implemented}} to physically improve the number and quality of visitors to a website<span style=\"\">&nbsp; </span>and the site&#39;s rankings within a search engine.| To improve a site&#39;s ranking and its quality and number of visitors Search engine optimization techniques are used.}} {{The {{goal |aim | target}} of SEO services is to make the site content search engine friendly and fulfill the criteria to gain a better ranking.| The various SEO services are applied together to improve the site&#39;s content and to make it SEO friendly and ultimately to improve the site&#39;s ranking}}. It is a challenging {{task | job}} for {{site owners | webmasters}}, SEO companies play an {{integral | important | vital}} role in optimizing a site with all of the major search engines.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>\r\n	<o:p></o:p>How search engines work<o:p><br />\r\n	</o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	You {{must | need}} to have an {{comprehension | understanding}} of how a search engine works. {{When a user seeks information the user searches the web using his favourite search engine.| Any user searches the web for information through search engines.}} The search keyword varies a great deal and, in today&#39;s crowded web world, could be found in countless pages. {{Sites are ranked i order to show then in a proper order. | Thanks to this, sites need to be ranked in order to show them in a uniform fashion.}}<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<o:p></o:p>Search engines have different criteria whilst these can vary from engine to engine, there are standards that most prescribe t